                    — 2024, c. 17, s. 315</TitleText></Heading><Section><MarginalNote><XRefExternal reference-type="regulation" link="SOR-2012-146">Cost Recovery Regulations</XRefExternal></MarginalNote><Label>315</Label><Text>The <XRefExternal reference-type="regulation" link="SOR-2012-146">Cost Recovery Regulations</XRefExternal>, as they read on August 27, 2019, registered as SOR/2012-146, are deemed to be made by the Governor in Council, under section 109 of the amended Act, on the commencement day.</Text></Section></RelatedOrNotInForce></RegulationPiece></Schedule></Regulation>